column1: Baby Barnaby's////I highly recommend the Green Eggs plate--two eggs scrambled with spinach
column5: fried potatoes.  This and the self-serve carafe of coffee on the table put some pep in my step.  Though ensconced in smaller quarters than Barnaby's
column6: the place did not feel crowded. The waitstaff also couldn't be more efficient and nice (another reason I am returning).
